</div></figure>
<ul><li>延伸阅读：<a href="https://chickensoupfamily.com/2020/06/20/earlyadulthood/">最适合华人家庭的「相依性独立」怎麼做？</a></li><li>延伸阅读：<a href="https://chickensoupfamily.com/2020/09/11/parent-child-power-reversal/">亲子权力反转－成年子女可能需要「不太乖」</a></li></ul>
